cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a method for improving object detection accuracy in autonomous driving applications, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves modeling the bounding box with a Gaussian parameter and redesigning the loss function, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a method for predicting localization uncertainty, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE.
